OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1784321281
OL,3,CTemperatures above 30C for 12th day in
OL,4,Ca row as heatwave continues
OL,6,FTemperatures in the UK on Thursday
OL,7,Fpeaked at 30.6C at Merryfield in
OL,8,FSomerset, the Met Office said, making
OL,9,Fit the 12th day in a row when 30C has
OL,10,Fbeen exceeded somewhere in the country.
OL,12,FThere were 18 consecutive days of 30C-
OL,13,Fplus temperatures in the punishingly
OL,14,Fhot year of 1976, when drought
OL,15,Fconditions damaged crops, scorched
OL,16,Flandscapes and forced people to use
OL,17,Fstandpipes in the street.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
