FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1784321281
OL,3,CTemperatures above 30C for 12th day in
OL,4,Ca row as heatwave continues
OL,6,FSeveral water companies have already
OL,7,Fintroduced hosepipe bans, impacting
OL,8,Fmillions of Brits.
OL,10,FWhether the current heatwave continues
OL,11,Fwill depend on whether there are three
OL,12,Fdays of temperatures above 28C in
OL,13,FLondon or 25C for the rest of the
OL,14,Fcountry.
OL,16,FIt comes as Britons have so far coped
OL,17,Fwith a sweltering summer of above-
OL,18,Faverage temperatures and persistently
OL,19,Fwarm nights.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
