OL,3,CTemperatures above 30C for 12th day in
OL,4,Ca row as heatwave continues
OL,6,FEngland has been particularly warm,
OL,7,Fwith mean temperatures currently 2.4C
OL,8,Fabove the average 21C that could be
OL,9,Fexpected.
OL,11,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
